    "This was not the case for peak wrist velocity (placing phase) and movement time (placing phase) datasets, that were rather characterised by a positively skewed distribution.",
    "For their analysis, we fitted a Generalised Linear Mixed-Effects Model using the function glmer of the \"lme4 1.1-23\" package (Bates et al. 2015).",
    "We used the Gamma family for characterising the distribution of the dependent variable and the log link function to define the relationship between the fixed factors and the dependent variable.",
    "\"You\" and 10 \"Him\", presented in a randomised order), for a total of 160 trials.",
    "A short pause of 1 min was provided at the end of each block of trials."
